1. Create a database and import the included SQL files.
2. Rename the config.php.dist file in app/system to config.php
3. Edit the .htaccess file to enable SSL (optional).
4. Edit the config.php file:-
    a. ARCDBSERVER - database server
    b. ARCDBNAME - database name
    c. ARCDBUSER - database username
    d. ARCDBPASSWORD - database password
    e. ARCDBTYPE - database type
    f. ARCDBPREFIX - table prefix, no change required
    g. ARCDEBUG - enable/disable debug mode
    h. ARCSESSIONTIMEOUT - session timeout
    i. ARCFORCENOSSL - force SSL off
    j. ARCIVKEYPAIR - Encryption key, MUST BE CHANGED
5. Login to site with 'admin@server.local' and 'password'
